Title: Fall in Love at First Kiss
Writer: Kaoru Tada (manga), Yung-Ting Tseng (screenplay), Yu Shan Chen (screenplay), Chi-Jou Huang (screenplay)
Actors: Talu Wang, Yun Lin, Kenji Chen, Cecilia Choi
Plot: Adapted from Japanese manga series "Itazura na Kiss", about a teen girl who falls in love with her fellow senior since their first day of high school.
